a. For insert operation: O(1) (As insertion 'push' in a stack takes constant time)
b. For delete operation: O(1) (As deletion 'pop' in a stack takes constant time)
c. For 'Get Min' operation: O(1) (As we have used an auxiliary stack which has it's top as the minimum element)

